ComicInfo.Title: Sheena Queen of the Jungle
ComicInfo.Summary: In the big city and on the run from the corrupt Cardwell Industries, Sheena finds herself needing a disguise... And in this case, hiding in plain sight is her only choice! She's survived everything that the brutal jungle has thrown at her in her life... can she survive cocktail dresses, high heels and clutch purses?!
